name: GCP CloudSQL PostgreSQL with outdated engine versions
query: { cloudSqlInstances (where: { OR: [ {engine: "postgres"}, {engine: "postgresql"} ] engineVersion_NOT_IN: ["10", "11", "12", "13", "14", "15"] }) { identifier accountID cloudAccountID cloudAccountName cloudProvider idFromProvider internalAssetType internalName internalRegion assetCategory } }
